title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 64] Glam Rock, AOR, New Wave
description:
Ok....make some room on your ipods, some old new stuff to enjoy! of course if you don't already have them. From the AOR sound of Adrenalin, to Glam Rock of Mr. Adrian Borland & Co, digging into heavenly rock sound of Cretones to the new wave/rock goodness of Australian band, The Venetians, there's so much to discover! enjoy and don't forget to seed.  


Adrenalin - Road of the Gypsy [1986]

Adrian Borland & The Citizens - Alexandria [1989]

Cretones - Snap! Snap! [1981]

The Venetians - Calling In The Lions [1986]
